        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 66. Cnemaspis vandeventeri from Phuket Island, Phuket Province, Thailand. Upper right: adult male (LSUDPC 4362) in the dark color pattern phase. Photograph by H. Bringsoe. Lower right: juvenile (LSUDPC 8541) from Ranong Province in the light color pattern phase. Left: vegetative microhabitat on Phuket Island with a potential predator Dryocalamus subannulatus Duméril, Bibron & Duméril, 1854 (striped pattern phase). Photographs by MS." ;
